{"tid":1469933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要說：你是鬼；試著說：多謝警察/公安同志支持反送中運動","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:12.000Z","uid":6363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6800b88a3964a98d0a80ba033217c53f99388d","tid":1469933,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不捉鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e0627edb9c6b922f960d44e75e35519a9cacf82b","tid":1469933,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"（長文）仲記唔記得咩叫兄弟爬山同不割𥱊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b0012d31ca12b72eea648d33eb53bcf649be2c0","tid":1469933,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3dcca6038815b56a9f1add8f2a3f510c36ca08","tid":1469933,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"［前機場職員話你知 x 勸世文] 驕 兵 必 敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468780</a><br />\n- 